H. No. 1126 / 55 OG No. 26, 4804 (June 29, 1959)

[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 2201, May 07, 1959 ]

ACT CREATING CERTAIN BARRIOS IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF DAPITAN, PROVINCE OF ZAMBOANGA DEL NORTE.

Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:

SECTION 1. The following sitios in the Municipality of Dapitan, Province of Zamboanga del Norte, are constituted into barrios, to wit:

The sitios of Urap and Talisay to be known as the barrio of Oro;

The sitios of San Francisco, Villa Trinidad and Sigayan to be known as the barrio of San Francisco;

The sitios of Sicayab, Larayan, Pagatpatan, Boton and Aligway Island to be known as the barrio of Sicayab;

The sitio of Napo to be known as the barrio of Napo;

The sitio of Oyan to be known as the barrio of Oyan;

The sitio of Tag-olo to be known as the barrio of Tag-olo; and

The sitio of Aseniero to be known as the barrio of Aseniero.

SEC. 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Enacted without executive approval, May 7, 1959.
